com.btc.redg.generator.extractor

Class TableExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.btc.redg.generator.extractor.TableExtractor

  • public class TableExtractor
extends Object
    This class provides methods to extract a TableModel from a Table. It offers static methods for dealing with join tables as well.

      • extractTableModel

        public TableModel extractTableModel(schemacrawler.schema.Table table)
        Extracts the table model from a single table. Every table this table references via foreign keys must be fully loaded, otherwise an exception will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        table - The table to extract the model from
        Returns:
        The extracted model with all information needed for code generation

      • isJoinTable

        public static boolean isJoinTable(schemacrawler.schema.Table table)
        Uses heuristics to determine whether a table is a join table.

        A table is identified as a join table if every column is part of a foreign key or part of the primary key. Furthermore the primary may only consist of a single column or every column has to be part of a foreign key.

        Parameters:
        table - The table to check
        Returns:
        true if the table is probably a join table, false otherwise

      • analyzeJoinTable

        public static Map<String,Map<schemacrawler.schema.Table,List<String>>> analyzeJoinTable(schemacrawler.schema.Table table)
        Analyzes a join table and returns information about the foreign key relationships in this table

        Example:

        If the passed table is table ABC that is a join table for the m:n:o relation between tables A, B and C, the method will return 

             - A :
          - ABC :
                 - B
                 - C
     - B :
          - ABC :
                 - A
                 - C
     - C :
          - ABC :
                 - A
                 - B
        This information should be read as "A has a relation to B and C via the table ABC" and so on
        Parameters:
        table -
        Returns:
